<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Coffee Date? ☕</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: #1a0a00;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    position: relative;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* Steam particles */
  .steam {
    position: fixed;
    width: 4px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: steamUp ease-in infinite;
    background: rgba(255,200,130,0.3);
  }
  @keyframes steamUp {
    0% { transform: translateY(0) scaleX(1); opacity: 0; }
    30% { opacity: 0.6; }
    100% { transform: translateY(-200px) scaleX(2); opacity: 0; }
  }

  /* Warm glow bg */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(200,100,0,0.12), transparent 70%);
    bottom: 10%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .page {
    max-width: 640px;
    width: 100%;
    animation: riseIn 1s ease forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }
  @keyframes riseIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(50px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .cup-wrap {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 90px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    animation: wobble 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(200,120,0,0.5));
  }
  @keyframes wobble {
    0%,100% { transform: rotate(-3deg) scale(1); }
    50% { transform: rotate(3deg) scale(1.05); }
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 7vw, 4rem);
    color: #ffb347;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    text-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(255,179,71,0.3);
  }

  .sub {
    text-align: center;
    color: #a07050;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .invite-card {
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #2a1500, #1e0e00);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,179,71,0.2);
    border-radius: 28px;
    padding: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,179,71,0.1);
  }

  .invite-card p {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #f5deb3;
    line-height: 1.85;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .invite-card strong {
    color: #ffb347;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }
  .divider::before, .divider::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,179,71,0.3), transparent);
  }
  .divider span { font-size: 1.1rem; }

  /* Details */
  .details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .detail-box {
    background: rgba(255,179,71,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,179,71,0.15);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 20px 14px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .detail-box:hover {
    background: rgba(255,179,71,0.12);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }
  .detail-box .icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 8px; display: block; }
  .detail-box .label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #a07050; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .detail-box .value { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #ffb347; font-weight: 500; }

  /* Big question */
  .question-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c85000, #8b2500);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 36px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 15px 45px rgba(200,80,0,0.35);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .question-card::before {
    content: '☕';
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 140px;
    opacity: 0.06;
    bottom: -20px;
    right: -10px;
  }
  .question-card h2 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .question-card p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* Yes/No buttons */
  .btn-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-yes {
    padding: 18px 55px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffb347, #e67e00);
    color: #1a0a00;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(230,126,0,0.45);
  }
  .btn-yes:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.05);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(255,179,71,0.55);
  }

  .btn-no {
    padding: 18px 45px;
    background: transparent;
    color: #a07050;
    border: 1px solid rgba(160,112,80,0.3);
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Yes message overlay */
  .yes-msg {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(26,10,0,0.95);
    z-index: 99;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
  }
  .yes-msg.show { display: flex; animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease; }
  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }
  .yes-msg h2 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: #ffb347;
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .yes-msg p {
    color: #f5deb3;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 400px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media(max-width:480px) {
    .details { grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); }
    .btn-yes, .btn-no { padding: 16px 35px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<script>
  for(let i=0;i<12;i++){
    const s=document.createElement('div');
    s.className='steam';
    const h=30+Math.random()*60;
    s.style.cssText=`height:${h}px;left:${30+Math.random()*40}%;bottom:${10+Math.random()*20}%;animation-duration:${2+Math.random()*3}s;animation-delay:${Math.random()*3}s;`;
    document.body.appendChild(s);
  }
</script>

<!-- Yes overlay -->
<div class="yes-msg" id="yesMsg">
  <div style="font-size:80px">🥰☕</div>
  <h2>Yay! It's a Date!</h2>
  <p>Get ready, Azhagi — I'll pick the best café, order your favourite, and I promise to make you laugh all evening. I can't wait! 💕</p>
</div>

<div class="page">

  <div class="cup-wrap">☕</div>

  <h1>Coffee Date,<br>Azhagi?</h1>
  <p class="sub">A warm invitation, just for you</p>

  <div class="invite-card">
    <p>
      Life is too short for bad coffee and unresolved fights.<br>
      Let me sit across from you, stare into your beautiful eyes,<br>
      and remind you why <strong>you are my favourite person</strong>.<br><br>
      Just you, me, and two warm cups ☕
    </p>

    <div class="divider"><span>☕</span></div>

    <p style="font-size:1rem; color:#a07050;">
      "Every love story is beautiful, but ours is my favourite —<br>especially over coffee."
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="details">
    <div class="detail-box">
      <span class="icon">📍</span>
      <div class="label">Where</div>
      <div class="value">Your favourite café</div>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-box">
      <span class="icon">🕔</span>
      <div class="label">When</div>
      <div class="value">Whenever you say</div>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-box">
      <span class="icon">💕</span>
      <div class="label">With</div>
      <div class="value">Your boy 🫶</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="question-card">
    <h2>So… will you go on a coffee date with me? ☕</h2>
    <p>One cup of coffee, a lot of love, and forever to make it up to you.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="btn-row">
    <button class="btn-yes" onclick="document.getElementById('yesMsg').classList.add('show')">Yes, I'd love that! 🥰</button>
    <button class="btn-no" onmouseover="this.style.right='200px';this.style.position='relative'" onmouseout="this.style.right='0'">No 😒</button>
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>